verbose_text: In a study from our country performed by Gunal et al., which evaluated the association between serum quantitative HBsAg, ALT and HBV DNA levels in HBeAg negative CHB infection, patients were divided into two groups according to HBV DNA levels,> 2000 IU/ml (50/99) and < 2000 IU/ml (49/99), and comparison between quantitative HBsAg levels and ALT, HBV DNA was performed.
